The '''7th constituency of the Bas-Rhin''' is a French legislative [[Constituency (France)|constituency]] in the [[Bas-Rhin]] [[departments of France|''département'']].

==Description==

Bas-Rhin's 7th Constituency covers the north western portion of [[Bas Rhin]] and includes all of the [[Arrondissement of Saverne]] as well as [[Hochfelden, Bas-Rhin|Hochfelden]] from the [[Arrondissement of Strasbourg-Campagne]]. It also includes the southern portion of the [[Northern Vosges Regional Natural Park]].

Like much of [[Alsace]] the constituency has returned conservative members to the [[National Assembly of France|National Assembly]] throughout the [[French Fifth Republic|Fifth Republic]].

